-- HudBay Names Former Agnico Finance Chief Garofalo as New Chief Executive
-- JoAnne Norton
-- 2010-06-21T10:35:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-21/hudbay-names-former-agnico-finance-chief-garofalo-as-new-chief-executive.html

          
          
             HudBay Minerals Inc. said it had
named David Garofalo as president and chief executive officer.
He also will be a director. Garofalo is a former senior vice
president and chief financial officer at Agnico-Eagle Mines Ltd.  
          
          


  


        